      <div class="msgContentFrame">Just as the title states. I really need help with this because it doesnt make any sense. I have the blacksmithing tools. which allow me to do armorsmithing quest. I go to synthesis and theres no list of what i can make. it just allows me to add materials. this is one confusing game. I like it alot just getting started is the hard part I am not sure what to do and how to do it. I have tried playing the game. and I am up to an gladiator rank 9 MINer rank 8 and a blacksmith rank 3. Thats easy just do the levequest. but when it comes to making items it just doesnt make any sense. I try to do a quest for that and it says I havent gotten the items yet or I dont have enough of the items. and if I do find one where I have the items for it it says I have to turn it in to an npc. how do i know where that npc is. My starting area is LL. Any and all info you could give to help me figure this out would be much appreciated. <br /> <br /> Because of another post I was able to figure out how to synthesis items for quest like click on requested items then click the quest hit commence then main hand. I know how to synthesis things also. But then your supposed to turn the quest in. How do you know where that npc is. It could be anywhere. <br /> <br /></div>
