      <div class="msgContentFrame">to make your own armor, you just have to be the correct rank of the correct craft for what you want to make.  <br /> <br />now for the NPC, if you go to your journal &gt; local quest.... you can look over your current local leves and it will tell you which NPC you need to go to and the general area like lower limsa, or camp bloodshore. now aside from asking your friends, LS mates..... you can google the NPCs name normally like this    FFXIV NPC and it will bring up wikis with the location of that NPC then you just go find them and talk to them <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=1832836" rel="external nofollow" title="lodestone.finalfantasyxiv.com/rc/character/status?cicuid=1832836"><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1815809.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /></a> <br /></div></div>
